$interpreted: Tindoiimu: Gyah...!!
Tingko: Sir! Your hand is bleeding—!!
Younger Jackal: Heh~ Seems like my big bro' roughed up your master a little bit.
Tingko: Leave him alone!!
Sophie: Hutchinson!
Older Jackal: More backup, huh? What a pain.
Older Jackal: Don't think you can mess with us! You just wait and see!
Sophie: Hutchinson, are you alright?

Hutchinson: I thought I was done for back there, but...
Thank you both for helping me.
Sophie: Yes, thank you both so much for saving Hutch—Yah!!

Sophie: You're hurt! You're losing a lot of blood...
Quick, come to our tent. I'll patch you up!
Tindoiimu: It's okay, it's just a scratch. Nothing to worry about.
Hanbei: What do you mean 'scratch'!? You're going pale! You'll pass out if we don't do anything!
Tindoiimu: No, really I don't want to bother you—
Sophie: Bother!? It's no bother! You saved Hutchinson's life!
Tingko: Sir, why don't we just let them bandage you up?
Tindoiimu: (Maybe she's right... If I went back to my room like this, it would definitely draw some attention...)
Tindoiimu: Then... very well.
Sophie: Come with me!
Sophie: Good thing we're always hurting ourselves while practicing, so we're all stocked up with medicine and bandages.
Tindoiimu: Ungh...
Sophie: Ah! I'm sorry, did I hurt you!?
Tindoiimu: No, no... Thank you for taking care of me.
Tindoiimu: And thank you for saving us back there.
Sophie: No, I should really be thanking you two...
Sophie: Hutchinson told me that you both really stuck your necks out back there...
Hanbei: Yo, Sophie! This permit is important, you should be keeping an eye on it!
Tingko: Eh, this has the official qilin seal on it...
Sophie: We've really sacrificed a lot to be able to perform here in qilin territory. It took a lot of effort.
Hanbei: And a lot of money!
Ru-yi: And a lot of time! It took months to get that permit...
Sophie: But it is what it is... gotta play by the rules!
Sophie: Sorry, let me properly introduce myself. My name's Sophie Lee. I'm ringmaster of Morgan's Marvelous Circus!
Tindoiimu: My name's... Tim, and she's my servant.
Tingko: Hi Sophie! My name's... Ying.
Sophie: And this is my team—Ru-yi the whale, Hanbei the hedgehog, and that's Hutchinson.
Sophie: We're on a world tour!!
Tindoiimu: On tour? So then you must have seen a lot of places?
Sophie: We have! And we've brought smiles to them all.
Hanbei: Hmph... Yeah, and I would have rather gone to any of those places a second time, but no, you just had to drag us to the East Alliance...
Hanbei: And now look at us! We've got no audience, and someone tried to beat Hutchinson up!
Hutchinson: I'm really sorry to worry everybody...

Ru-yi: I'm... I'm a bit scared, really~
What if I... what if I run into those whales that used to make fun of my blowhole...
Sophie: Listen, I really want to see Ru-yi and Hanbei's hometown. And I want to show the east what we're all about. I want them to like us!

Sophie: I never thought it would be this hard.
And now we've got that theater troupe hounding us every chance they get...
Tindoiimu: Are they really always bothering you?
Sophie: Yeah, that whole troupe hates us. They think we're stealing their business, I guess...
Sophie: But no point feeling down about it! I know I'll find a way to make everyone love us!
Sophie: I've got to make them smile!
Tindoiimu: (This girl... she looks even younger than me... but she's brave enough to face all these hardships...)
Tindoiimu: You know, people from the alliance tend to be a bit traditional. Your circus might just be too new for them. It scares them.
Tindoiimu: ...Why not try to mix a little of their own culture into your performance?
Sophie: Hmm... mix in their own culture...
Sophie: So I should get to know the alliance a bit and bring their style into our show? You think they would work?
Tindoiimu: That's just my suggestion, if it helps...
Sophie: It sounds like a great idea!
Sophie: So maybe we should start from the props...
Tingko: Sir, we should probably be getting back.
Tindoiimu: Oh right... I'm very sorry, we need to head home.
Tindoiimu: Thank you for bandaging me up, and good luck with your performance.
Sophie: Ah...
Sophie: H-Hold on!
Sophie: I... uh... will we see each other again?
Sophie: Actually, I... I have a lot of questions about the East Alliance. I was hoping I could maybe ask you?
Tindoiimu: Sure, I'll come back again soon.
